Issue:

Notice that tool_calls contains only one entry combining both get_weather and get_news, instead of two separate entries.

The id field is concatenated with <|tool_call_begin|> and <|tool_call_end|> markers, which may indicate a parsing/regex issue in the Kimi-K2 tool parser.

